<div class='col-sm-12'>
  <h4>{{t "AAC Modeling" key="aac_modeling"}}</h4>
</div>
<div class='col-sm-12'>
  <div class="setup-modeling-demo">
    <img src={{path "images/board-modeling.png"}} alt="" class="setup-modeling-demo__img" >
    <div class="setup-modeling-demo__circle" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="setup-modeling-demo__rect" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class='col-sm-12' style="margin-top: 16px;">
  <ul class="usage-checklist">
    <li class="usage-checklist__item">{{t "Modeling means showing the communicator how to use their device — tap the buttons yourself so they can learn by watching." key="modeling_1"}}</li>
    <li class="usage-checklist__item">{{t "To start Modeling Mode, tap the options button (three dots) and select \"Model for Communicator.\"" key="modeling_2"}}</li>
    <li class="usage-checklist__item">{{t "While modeling, your taps are tracked separately so they don't appear in the communicator's usage reports." key="modeling_3"}}</li>
    <li class="usage-checklist__item">{{t "When you're done, open the options menu again and select \"Stop Modeling\" to return to normal mode." key="modeling_4"}}</li>
  </ul>
</div>
